  "title": "Research & Development Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></p><ul><li><p>Research on concepts to innovate and improve existing/new products</p></li><li><p>Plan, design and develop products within quality target and cost</p></li><li><p>Consolidate design input and develop schedule of conceptual design for Manager’s approval</p></li><li><p>Participate in Innovate Project Team Projects - Execute basic R&D projects</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement :</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree Mechanical or Eletrical/Eletronics Engineer</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
